snippet.title: METAL GEAR SOLID SNAKE EATER 3D - E3 2011 Trailer
snippet.description:
METAL GEAR SOILD 3 SNAKE EATER is the origin of the METAL GEAR Saga and is lauded as one of the best in the series.  While remaining true to the original story and game system, METAL GEAR SOLID SNAKE EATER 3D features a host of  unique new features that can only be realized on the Nintendo 3DS.  Don't miss the latest trailer for METAL GEAR SOLID SNAKE EATER 3D!  Coming this winter.

[ Official Site]
http://www.konami.jp/mgs_se/
